1. *Bi* li mogao da mi pomogneš? (Would you be able to help me?)
2. *Bila* bih ti zahvalna. (I would be grateful to you.)
3. *Bi* li želeo da se vratim? (Would you like me to come back?)
4. *Bila* bih spremna da počnem. (I would be ready to start.)
5. *Bi* li mogao da mi daš neke savete? (Would you be able to give me some advice?)